<%-
  scope = 'page_titles.school.donated_devices.interest.disclaimer'
  title = t('title', scope: scope)
%>
<%- content_for :title, title %>
<%- content_for :before_content do %>
  <%- school_breadcrumbs items: title, school: @school, user: @current_user %>
<%- end %>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    <h1 class="govuk-heading-xl">
      <%= title %>
    </h1>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Computers For Kids is a Mail Force initiative. Itâ€™s separate from the Department for Education (DfE) and the Get Help with Technology programme.
    </p>
    <p class="govuk-body">
    If you opt in to Computers for Kids, your details will be shared with Mail Force and its third party supplier.
    </p>
    <p class="govuk-body">
    Devices will be allocated by the third party supplier on a first come, first served basis. These devices are refurbished by the third party supplier to industry standard security and safety regulations.
    </p>
    <p class="govuk-body">
    School, colleges, trusts and responsible bodies need to make sure that devices are suitable for children and young people.
The DfE does not provide any guarantee or warranty for the reliability, suitability or completeness of the devices, and/or related software, or third party service.
    </p>
    <h2 class="govuk-heading-m"><%= t('not_responsible', scope: scope) %></h2>
    <p class="govuk-body">
    The DfE is not responsible for the currency, security, availability, compatibility, suitability, reliability or freedom from damaging software, or for any other qualities or features of the devices, and/or related software, and third party service.
    </p>
    <p class="govuk-body">
    It is also not responsible for any actions taken with the devices and/or related software, or how the devices are used.
    </p>
    <p class="govuk-body govuk-!-margin-bottom-7">
    The DfE is not liable for any loss or damage that might come from the devices, and/or related software, or third party service.
    </p>
    <%= form_for @form, url: address_donated_devices_school_path(@school), method: :post do |f| %>
      <%= f.govuk_error_summary %>
      <% @form.device_types.compact_blank.each do |dt| %>
        <%= f.hidden_field :device_types, multiple: true, value: dt %>
      <% end %>
      <%= f.hidden_field :units %>
      <%= f.govuk_submit 'Continue' %>
    <%- end %>
  </div>
</div>
